

# First line should be a single sentence summarizing the change.
# 
# Leave a blank line between the summary sentence and a longer description.
# The longer description should include:
# 
# * Why you are making this change
# * How the change works, i.e. what it does differently after the change
# * Any problems, immediate or potential, with this change
# * If the change is associated with a bug, issue, or ticket, include the #
#
# Take your time and write a helpful commit message. This is not something 
# that you hammer out in 30 seconds right before you deploy something, this is 
# part of the process of writing quality applications.
